VSAP-Client-Config version 0.01
===============================

This module provides a central location to define how the VSAP::Client 
works on a particuluar platform. Different VSAP::Client::Config modules
would be created for each architecture. They would control the options
such as the port being used, unix domain sockets, or TCP, etc. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

none.

